  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイル、なにかいる？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kyle, do you need something?
(TLN: This is a pun on Kyle's name. His katakana spells his name as "Ka i ru". Cless' question in
hiragana ends in "ka i ru".)</EnglishText>
      <Notes>I've left this in the translation itself as well, but this is a pun on Kyle's name. I'm not sure how else to even translate this without completely changing the pun, which would also defeat the purpose of the pun and ultimately make no sense without changing the entire conversation.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？　なに急に？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Why are you asking, all of a sudden?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイル、なにかいるんじゃないかい？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kyle, you need something, don't you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>い、いらないよ！
知らない人から物をもらっちゃいけないって
父さんが言ってた！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I-I don't need anything!
My dad told me never to
take anything from a stranger!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>悪いな。
今こいつちょっと残念な事になっててよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Sorry.
He's doing something really dreadful right now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>たしかに残念だわ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It really is dreadful...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なぜわかってくれないんだ！？
僕はカイルに物をあげたいだけなのに！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why don't you get it?!
I'm just trying to give something to you!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いらないって言ってるだろ！
そんなに言うんだったら……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I told you I don't need anything!
If you keep asking that...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……そうだね。　戦うしかない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...That's right.
There will be nothing to do but fight it out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>本気かよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>They're seriously doing it...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
